#import "lib.typ": *

== Takeout Doubles

Equal level conversion only over 1#M openings with o#M and #D, see #ref(<def:1M-X>, supplement: none).

== Against Strong 1#C

#bt(```
  DBL    MM
  `n`N   mm
```)

== Against 1$X$ natural

#bt(```
  2X over 1m   MM, 55+
  2X over 1M   oM and m, 55+
  2N           two lowest unbid suits (at least 55)
```)

=== (1#M)—#pass—(2#M)—#dbl—

#bt(```
  (RDBL)
    system on
  2S           5+S, below INV
  2N           _Lebensohl_ (usually puppet to 3C)
    (DBL)
      system on
    3C        usually forced
      PASS         below INV, C suit
      3X below M   5+X, below INV
      3M           asks 4 card oM, with stopper
      3X above M   5+X, INV
      3N           to play, with stopper
    3DHS 4C   18+, 5+ strong suit
    3N        18+, semiBAL, with stopper
  3X below M   5+X, INV
  3M           asks 4 card oM, no stopper
  3X above M   5+X, GF
  3N           to play, no stopper
  4X below M   5+X, GF
```)

=== (1#M)—#dbl— <def:1M-X>

#bt(```
  2C
    2D   _Equal Level Conversion_, oM and D
```)

=== (1#M)—#dbl—(2#M)—

#bt(```
  DBL          responsive
  2S           5+S, below INV
  2N           _Lebensohl_ (usually puppet to 3C)
    (DBL)
      system on
    3C        usually forced
      PASS         below INV, C suit
      3X below M   5+X, below INV
      3M           asks 4 card oM, with stopper
      3X above M   5+X, INV
      3N           to play, with stopper
    3DHS 4C   18+, 5+ strong suit
    3N        18+, semiBAL, with stopper
  3X below M   5+X, INV
  3M           asks 4 card oM, no stopper
  3X above M   5+X, GF
  3N           to play, no stopper
  4X below M   5+X, GF
```)

== Against 1#D precision

1#D is treated as a natural 1$X$ opening with the following exceptions. This means that #D is used for cue bids later even though it is not used in the first overcall.

#bt(```
  DBL   short D not needed
  1N    does not promise a D stopper
* 2D    natural
  2H    _Michaels cue_, 55+ SH
  2N    _Unusual_, 55+ HC
* 3D    _Super-Michaels_, 55+ SH, F1
```)

== Against 1#N <sec:v1N>

#bt(```
  DBL   penalty
  2C    54+ MM
  2D    6+ M
  2H    5H + 4+m
  2S    5S + 4+m
  2N    55+ mm
```)

== Against 2#m majors

#bt(```
  DBL   4+M
  2H    54+ mm, C better
  2S    54+ mm, D better
```)

== Against weak 2$X$

#bt(```
  DBL            { 12+, 3+ cards in unbid suits, shortness in X / 18+, 5+ strong suit = rebid suit / 18+, semiBAL, with stopper = rebid N }
    (RDBL)
      system on
    2Y           5+Y, below INV
    2N           _Lebensohl_ (usually puppet to 3C)
      (DBL)
        system on
      3C        usually forced
        PASS         below INV, C suit
        3Y below X   5+Y, below INV
        3X           asks a 4 card M, with stopper
        3Y above X   5+Y, INV
        3N           to play, with stopper
      3DHS 4C   18+, 5+ strong suit
      3N        18+, semiBAL, with stopper
    3Y below X   5+Y, INV
    3X           asks 4 card M, no stopper
    3Y above X   5+Y, GF
    3N           to play, no stopper
    4Y below X   5+Y, GF
  2Y             10--17, 5+ cards
*   (3X)
*     DBL   responsive, 10+, length in unbid suits, no support for Y
*   PASS      0--7
*   3X        strong raise in Y, GF
*   3Y        8--10, 3+ Y
*   3Z        5+ suit, F1
*   4 not Y   splinter
  2N             14--17, semiBAL, with stopper
* 3Y below X     12--17, (5)6+ cards
* 3Y above X     16+, very strong 6+ cards
  3X             stopper ask for N
  3N             16+, with stopper and a long-running minor
  4X             55+, mm
* 4m             55+, m and oM (or MM over 2D)
* 4HS if not X   16+ strong 6+ cards
```)

== Against precision 2#C

Treat as weak 2$X$.

== Against 2#N minors

#bt(```
  DBL   penalty interest in at least one minor
  3C    MM, H better
  3D    MM, S better
  3H    nat
  3S    nat
```)

== Against weak 3$X$

#bt(```
  DBL          { 14+, 3+ cards in unbid suits, shortness in X / 18+, 5+ strong suit = rebid suit / 23+, semiBAL, with stopper = rebid N }
  3Y           12--17, (5)6+ cards
  3N           16-22, with stopper
* 4X over m    55+, MM
* 4X over M    55+, oM + m
* 4m (not X)   55+, m + M (other or unspecified)
* 4M (not X)   16+ strong 6+ cards
* 4N over M    55+ mm
```)

== Against weak 4#m

#bt(```
* DBL        takeout
* 4N         natural with stopper(s)
* 5m (cue)   55+ MM
  other      natural
```)

== Against weak 4#H

#bt(```
  DBL     penalty-oriented
*     bid   5S or 6+ card suit
* 4N      55+ mm
  other   natural
```)

== Against weak 4#S

#bt(```
  DBL     penalty-oriented
*     bid   6+ card suit
* 4N      takeout
  other   natural
```)
